    "Note that here we used the term \"Critical Lure\" referring to all the new items falling within the close space defined by the Studied Items.",
    "When only one critical lure is selected this option gives the possibility to have this item as the one closest to the centroid of the Studied Items compared to any other item, as in classical DRM lists.",
